Package length

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Foot
    This subclass of Length represents the length supplied in the constructor in feet, with conversion abilities to meters.
    Inch
    This subclass of Length represents the length supplied in the constructor in inches, with conversion abilities to meters.
    Length
    A Length is an object that has a length and a unit, can be converted to meters, can be added to other Lengths, and can be compared to other Lengths.
    Meter
    This subclass of Length represents the length supplied in the constructor in meters.
    Yard
    This subclass of Length represents the length supplied in the constructor in yards, with conversion abilities to meters.
